s (Sur la calotte du couvercle et sur le bouchon fermant le bec. Poin\u00e7on des Menus ouvrages pour les ouvrages non charg\u00e9s 1er octobre 1717 - 15 f\u00e9vrier 1722)","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Longueur","value":"14,2","displayDimension":"14,2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Hauteur","value":"9,2","displayDimension":"9,2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"9,7","displayDimension":"9,7 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : c\u00e9ramique\r\nMat\u00e9riau : porcelaine\r\nMat\u00e9riau : or","placeOfCreation":"Chine (Asie-\u003EAsie orientale = Extr\u00eame Orient) ; Paris (France-\u003EIle-de-France = Ile de France)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Philippe d\u0027Orl\u00e9ans, r\u00e9gent du Royaume (1674-1723) sans doute offert \u00e0 son \u00e9pouse Fran\u00e7oise-Marie de Bourbon, duchesse d\u0027Orl\u00e9ans (1677-1749) ; collection David David-Weill ; vente Paris, Palais Galliera, 4 juin 1971, n\u00b0 70 ; galerie Jacques Kugel ; dation en paiement de droits du au titre d\u0027une donation partage, 2007","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"M. David-Weill, David","note":"","role":", Collectionneur"},{"value":"Bourbon, Marie-Fran\u00e7oise de","note":"","role":", Propri\u00e9taire"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"dation","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date du conseil","value":"20\/06\/2007","startYear":2007,"endYear":2007},{"type":"date de comit\u00e9\/commission","value":"10\/07\/2007","startYear":2007,"endYear":2007},{"type":"date de l\u0027arr\u00eat\u00e9\/d\u00e9cision","value":"21\/12\/2007","startYear":2007,"endYear":2007}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des 